General.Name: Baan Rock Garden Public Company Limited
General.Description: Baan Rock Garden Public Company Limited engages in the real estate development business in Thailand. It develops and sells townhouses, single detached houses, and commercial buildings under the Baan Rock Garden brand. The company was formerly known as Chucheep South Group, Co., Ltd. Baan Rock Garden Public Company Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
